<div class="help-content-wrap"><h3 id="how-to-rebet">How to Rebet</h3>
<h4 id="what-is-rebet-">What is Rebet?</h4>
<p>SportyBet has a brand new REBET feature that allows you to quickly reload open selections and place the bet again. The &quot;Rebet&quot; function is only available for &quot;Real Sports&quot;.</p>
<h4 id="how-can-i-rebet-">How can I Rebet?</h4>
<h5 id="rebet-on-ticket-details-page">Rebet on &quot;Ticket Details&quot; Page</h5>
<ul>
<li>Step 1: Log in to your account.</li>
<li>Step 2: Go to &quot;Bet History&quot; on the top-right corner.</li>
<li>Step 3: Find any running ticket you want to rebet on and go into the &quot;Ticket Details&quot; page.</li>
<li><p>Step 4: Click on &quot;Rebet&quot; button.</p>
<p>  <img src="../../../../assets/ng-pc-rebet-1.png" alt=""></p>
</li>
</ul>
<h5 id="rebet-on-submission-successful-page">Rebet on &quot;Submission Successful&quot; Page</h5>
<ul>
<li>Step 1: First, place a bet.</li>
<li>Step 2: After placing the bet, you will be redirected to the &quot;Submission Successful&quot; page.</li>
<li><p>Step 3: Click on the &quot;Rebet&quot; button.</p>
<p>  <img src="../../../../assets/ng-pc-rebet-2.png" alt=""></p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>